snippet.title: Johnny Depp Scores Win After Judge Rejects Amber's Suit Dismissal
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Scores Big Win Over Amber Heard As Judge Rejects Her Bid To Throw Out His Defamation Suit.

✅ SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiKzneRB4I4eTN_bHEqV-gg?sub_confirmation=1

After multiple fails, Johnny Depp has finally secured a win in the lawsuit scene against Amber Heard. He recently won $50 million given to him by a Virginia judge. The drama seems to never end after both spouses were accused of abusing each other.

#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard
